# EAS Builds

This project uses **interactive-only** EAS / Apple flows (see `interactive-workflows.mdc`). The agent must not use `--non-interactive` for `eas build` or related commands.

Always use interactive builds (never `--non-interactive`):

```bash
cd frontend && eas build --platform ios --profile production --auto-submit
```

- Never pass `--non-interactive` to `eas build`
- Always use `--auto-submit` to submit to TestFlight automatically
- Always bump `ios.buildNumber` in `frontend/app.json` before building and commit it
